text: Loïc Gagnon (born 21 January 1991) is a French footballer who plays as a winger.Liga II Round 12 teams. frf.ro ==Club career== ===Spartak Trnava=== Gagnon made his Fortuna Liga debut for Spartak Trnava against ŽP Šport Podbrezová on 17 July 2016.FO ŽP Šport Podbrezová - FC Spartak Trnava 17.07.2016, futbalnet.sk ==References== ==External links== * FC Spartak Trnava official club profile * Fortuna Liga profile * * Eurofotbal profile * Futbalnet profile Category:1991 births Category:Sportspeople from Bondy Category:Living people Category:French footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Slovak Super Liga players Category:Liga II players Category:Partizán Bardejov players Category:2.
